{"tid":176629,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪求] 政治哲學及實踐入門書嘅推介","createTime":"2017-03-28T09:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T07:36:29.000Z","uid":96129,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8358048e0e0d5dd2b0a09101de04a05ca65c6cf","tid":176629,"uid":96129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"見到香港宜家咁樣，除左覺得無力，更加覺得要增值自己。<br />\n平時同人討論都唔太敢出聲，因為覺得自己argument薄弱又無咩知識support，一直好想深化自己對唔同議題嘅認識同訓練思維，想理論同實踐都做好啲，唔想成廿歲人仲on99生勾勾。所以，在此跪求一啲好書/好網站/好片推介。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315e18b3dad7c34889fa846c5fa401ed72d926b6","tid":176629,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"政治的道德 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5621d813e1df6c985f946ce740a6ee3e4ffb2a38","tid":176629,"uid":93430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"Jonathan Wolff, An Introduction to Political Philosophy<br />\nDavid Miller, Political Philosophy: A Very Short Introduction<br />\nMichael J. Sandel, Justice: What's the Right Thing to Do<br />\nAdam Swift, Political Philosophy: A Beginner's Guide<br />\nWill Kymlicka, Contemporary Political Philosophy: An Introduction<br />\nRonald Dworkin, Justice for Hedgehogs<br />\n石元康，當代西方自由主義理論<br />\nIan Shapiro, The Moral Foundations of Politics<br />\nJason Brennan, Political Philosophy"},{"pid":"7b3dcd2d3b4f2d6f1fd45bdc554de74dd062e7b0","tid":176629,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"法國高中生哲學讀本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fd8bfe4a3bc44321404fe939478936d53972d3","tid":176629,"uid":96129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"推 可以嘅話可唔可以大概講下內容了解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcdf1e9e6875d96de239f930052b86f0162771e","tid":176629,"uid":93430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推 可以嘅話可唔可以大概講下內容了解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThey are all introductory texts of political philosophy. Their topics include political legitimacy, human rights, liberty, equality, democracy and so on.<br />\n<br />\nWhenever you want to know whether a book suits your interest, go to Amazon or download it somewhere. Check its table of content and skim its preface. You would then know which book suits you best."},{"pid":"962ff98fcb2eb014f263ec05d7488e13aa4384c3","tid":176629,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法國高中生哲學讀本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n顧名思義，係法國高中生所用教材，<br />\n難度唔會太深，方向主要係以政治道德為主。<br />\n本書有英美又有歐陸思想，相對平衡，<br />\n唔會太過偏向英美自由主義，應該唔錯。"},{"pid":"46f88b270376c3ff6478def69ab5e2938325d0d2","tid":176629,"uid":55922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"留名跟進 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e430085d51060e9fc4c882b097ca6b67a26851","tid":176629,"uid":96129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推 可以嘅話可唔可以大概講下內容了解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThey are all introductory texts of political philosophy. Their topics include political legitimacy, human rights, liberty, equality, democracy and so on.<