ets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知算唔算關事？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9d8d06ff3dd898f23e9c1135e3598947cceaee","tid":176629,"uid":55485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓上全部都係政治哲學<br />\n樓主話仲想要政治實踐既書，即係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我心目中係一啲幫助認識香港的唔同議題或者講本土/其他地方政治行動嘅書，例如如何抵抗<span style=\"color: red;\">資本主義</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，土地議題，霸權，等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知算唔算關事？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個睇成世都未必得<br />\n同埋睇呢d 真係歐陸關心既野多少少<br />\n英美都會涉及 但佢地關心既又唔係exactly呢種"},{"pid":"1ec7f6cb3d7003eb5d3457b8e4b634265319359e","tid":176629,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上全部都係政治哲學<br />\n樓主話仲想要政治實踐既書，即係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有匿名哲學家寫過幾本煽動性刊物：<br />\n好似《內戰導論》、《資本主義反抗宣言》等等<br />\n個淵源應該係來自於德勒茲，<br />\n傳聞德勒茲哲學係被應用於游擊戰......"},{"pid":"b5831171b5a7bbfdb211c62974db7b1696afe715","tid":176629,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓上全部都係政治哲學<br />\n樓主話仲想要政治實踐既書，即係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有匿名哲學家寫過幾本煽動性刊物：<br />\n好似《內戰導論》、《資本主義反抗宣言》等等<br />\n個淵源應該係來自於德勒茲，<br />\n傳聞德勒茲哲學係被應用於游擊戰......</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一講激進哲學，好多時英美哲學班人都會收聲。<br />\nIntroduction to Civil War 網上係有得 down。<br />\n<br />\n不過，如果想讀正正常常資本主義分析，<br />\n可以讀 World-Systems Analysis: An Introduction，<br />\n一本好短但足以了解資本主義運作的導論。"},{"pid":"0bf90267253db4738b8ec8740db4bb302b6fe629","tid":176629,"uid":55485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"